Merta Sterling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Merta_Sterling 0 Merta Sterling (June 13, 1883 – March 14, 1944) was an American film actress of the silent era. She appeared in 61 films between 1914 and 1927. She was born Manitowoc, Wisconsin and died in Hollywood, California.
